      "writtenOn": "2018-11-27T14:27:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t understand the third point.  Can you explain this in more detail?  IIUC in the above sequence, the callback would just run after s.Stop().  That\u0027s currently problematic because we don\u0027t check that the subscriber actually exists, but I\u0027ve fixed that in the next patchset.  So the callback would run and we\u0027d get a warning in the logs indicating that we don\u0027t know about that subscriber, and the message is dropped.",
      "parentUuid": "b429bc0d_a24974bc",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 118,
        "startChar": 11,
        "endLine": 118,
        "endChar": 19
      },
